OL,3,CPolice Chief says more officers needed
OL,4,Camid rising crime rate
OL,6,FJersey's Chief of Police says more
OL,7,Fofficers are needed and he is talking
OL,8,Fwith the Government about extra staff.
OL,10,FIt comes after the force's annual
OL,11,Freport was published, which shows that
OL,12,Fthe total number of crimes rose by 6%
OL,13,Flast year.
OL,15,FDespite this, the number of officers
OL,16,Fhas fallen from 215 in 2020 to 201 in
OL,17,F2024 - a figure lower per capita than
OL,18,FGuernsey, the Isle of Man and the UK.
