OL,3,CPolice Chief says more officers needed
OL,4,Camid rising crime rate
OL,6,F"There isn't a police chief I've ever
OL,7,Fworked with who wouldn't say he or she
OL,8,Fwants more police officers," Robin
OL,9,FSmith, the island's Chief of Police,
OL,10,Fsays.
OL,12,F"Of course I do and we're working with
OL,13,Fgovernment and officials to talk about
OL,14,Fthe numbers of police officers and
OL,15,Fvery importantly, police staff."
OL,17,FChief Officer Smith adds the force
OL,18,Fshould be optimistic about boosting
OL,19,Fnumbers, after their recruitment day
OL,20,Fsaw 150 people register interest.
