OL,3,CPolice Chief says more officers needed
OL,4,Camid rising crime rate
OL,6,FThey have whittled that number down to
OL,7,Ften prospective officers, who they are
OL,8,Flooking to fund for proper recruitment
OL,9,Fin the New Year.
OL,11,F"I'm very proud of that," he says.
OL,13,FAs for the rising crime figures, Chief
OL,14,FOfficer Smith adds that they do not
OL,15,Frepresent anything the island should
OL,16,Fbe significantly worried about.
OL,18,F"We have about 3,000 crimes a year so
OL,19,Fwe are a very, very low crime area,"
OL,20,Fhe explains.
