OL,3,CPolice Chief says more officers needed
OL,4,Camid rising crime rate
OL,6,F"That doesn't mean we're low demand,
OL,7,Fof course - only around 15% or 20% of
OL,8,Fwhat we do is actually related to
OL,9,Fcrime, what islanders would expect us
OL,10,Fto be dealing with.
OL,12,F"The other 80% involves concern for
OL,13,Fwelfare, mental health, low-level
OL,14,Fdisorderly behaviour that isn't
OL,15,Fbecoming a crime and we are working on
OL,16,Freducing that particular demand."
