OL,3,CPolice Chief says more officers needed
OL,4,Camid rising crime rate
OL,6,FThe report also broke down crime by
OL,7,Fproblem area - revealing that whilst
OL,8,Fdrug crimes fell by 32%, vehicle
OL,9,Fcrime, youth crimes and shoplifting
OL,10,Fall rose.
OL,12,FIt also detailed the number of
OL,13,Finvestigations relating to crimes
OL,14,Fagainst women and girls, which
OL,15,Fincreased by 10% since the creation of
OL,16,Fa specialist VAWG taskforce.
OL,18,FThe number of financial investigations
OL,19,Falso went up by 45%.
